Question: Shenzhen Chic Electrics Co., Ltd CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Shenzhen Chic Electrics Co., Ltd

Product: Jump Starters

- New arrival 3000A Jump Starter for all Gas/Diesel engines
- 12V Car Battery Jumper with Extended Jumper Cables
- 45W Fast Charging for phone, tablet, and laptop
- SOS, Strobe, Flashlight
- Water-resistant jump starter series available for testing purpose
- Showcased at CES 2024 in Las Vegas
- Face-to-face communication at CES remains crucial
- Booth No. 926, West Gate, CES 2024
